the UK and internationally, including at the Saatchi Gallery, NXT Museum, Lisbon Triennial, Istanbul Design Biennial, the Sundance Film Festival, and the V&A and Design Museum, London.\nBarnaby Steel – Artist and Director\nBarnaby Steel is an artist and co-founder of London based experiential studio Marshmallow Laser Feast. Barney's art steps outside the human centred worldview exploring the threads that weave us into relationships with the more than human world.", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2024-05-29T03:42:57.457109+10:00", "external_links": [], "uuid": "495643bc-e1fc-41fb-95be-959e5954c1e6", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "40698", "external_references": [], "date_modified": "2024-05-29T03:42:57.457340+10:00"}]}